Ecommerce App

 

Online Preview of Ecommerce App

Ecommerce App created using Ashera.

Ecommerce App is a sample application where in the user is able to place a order by using the app. He can also scan qr code placed at the table.

The app contains the following screens:

  • Splash
  • Login
  • Registration
  • Dashboard
  • Notification
  • Cart
  • Order List
  • Order Preview
